-- Bayer Posts $387 Million Net Income After Legal Costs, Missing Estimates
-- B y   P h i l   S e r a f i n o
-- 2010-10-28T05:35:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-28/bayer-posts-387-million-net-income-after-legal-costs-missing-estimates.html
Bayer AG reported third-quarter
profit of 280 million euros after setting aside 436 million
euros for litigation in U.S. The result missed the 494.5
million-euro average estimate of 15 analysts surveyed by
Bloomberg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
